Pyosra: A Python wrapper for OSRA
=================================


Description:
------------

- Pyosra is a Python wrapper that exposes the functionality of the OSRA structure
recognition tool to a Python environment, using pybind11. 

- It adds the capability to extract R-Group structures.

- Pyosra is designed to work in tandem with ChemSchematicResolver,a tool that can 
extract many chemical diagram and their descriptive labels directly from scientific
articles, in an automated fashion. 

- ChemSchematicResolver is open-source and documentation can be found at www.chemschematicresolver.org .
The source code can be found at https://github.com/edbeard/ChemSchematicResolver .

- The documentation for OSRA can be found at https://cactus.nci.nih.gov/osra/ .
